{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in this conversation, a member of the family [? or two ?] said, it's rumored that 2 million Jews have already been killed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother said, what's going to happen to all Jews is going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And something stirred in me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to myself, in my youthful bravura, if there's one Jew to survive, it will be me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, I was-- believed in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later, of course, I thought, how many others thought the same way?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it really, as future events show, you could have been the strongest, the healthiest, the cleverest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you didn't have the element of luck, luck, you wouldn't have survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's the game of the dice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, this was my little episode of the two episodes in the [INAUDIBLE] camp of Klaj.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A month or two later, unceremoniously, we were packed into a train and off we had to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never, they never gave us a reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Get into a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, we had-- yes, we had a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One thing I would like to-- I would like to sort of mention here that while we were back at the house, my father and I, he put his photograph into a jacket which he unfortunately forgot in the house.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we never returned there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one of the photographs was-- was lost already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, when we were on the train, there were only 150 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were not--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, two or three carriages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't sort of cramped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't go very far, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although we have learned-- we had learned already that-- we've heard, of course, about the SS and the camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't know much about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
